venv/

# Architecture artifacts
docs/delivery/*.json
docs/verification/*.json
!docs/delivery/.gitkeep
!docs/verification/.gitkeep

# Gate logs — tracked as audit-trail evidence (see docs/delivery/README.md).
# Maintainers should `git add gate/log/<new-sha>.json` after each gate run
# whose evidence will be referenced from a delivery file.
# (Was previously gitignored; reversed per user request to preserve all
# process artifacts on GitHub for future decision-making.)
